<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <style type="text/css">
    @import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:100,300,500|Roboto+Mono:100,300,500);
    @import url(https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/meyer-reset/2.0/reset.min.css);
    html,
    body {
      height: 100%;
    }
    body {
      text-align: center;
      background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
      background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #eef8dd 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #eef8dd 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #eef8dd 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #eef8dd 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    }
    body main {
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px;
      max-width: 540px;
    }
    body h1 {
      padding: 25px;
      font: 100 128px "Roboto", "Helvetica Neue", helvetica, sans-serif;
      line-height: 128px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -moz-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
      background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #7ec1a2 0%, #e6cea0 100%);
      background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #7ec1a2 0%, #e6cea0 100%);
      background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #7ec1a2 0%, #e6cea0 100%);
      background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #7ec1a2 0%, #e6cea0 100%);
    }
    body p {
      padding: 25px;
      font: 300 24px "Roboto Mono", courier, mono;
      color: #6a5036;
    }
    body p span {
      color: #c76b4b;
    }
    body p + p {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    body p a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #967ab4;
    }
    body p a:hover {
      color: #df94bd;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Cider Framework</title>
</head>
<body>
<main>

  <h1>Cider</h1>
  <p>Cider is nano (<span>no, really</span>) framework for small but, agile web applications.</p>
  <p>Fork, star and discuss at <a href="https://github.com/CarbinCreative/Cider" rel="external">Github</a>!</p>

</main>
</body></html>
